author: The Telegraph
title: Win England v Ireland rugby tickets
text: The Telegraph has teamed up with QBE Insurance to offer readers the chance to win two tickets to see England’s game against Ireland at Twickenham, the home of rugby, on Saturday, 5 September. The winner will receive a pair of tickets to the last of this season’s QBE Internationals, courtesy of QBE, Official Insurance Partner of England Rugby. Will coach Stuart Lancaster’s plans be foiled – or can captain Chris Robshaw and his men build vital momentum before the World Cup starts on 18 September? For the chance to win this superb prize, enter your details in the form below before midnight on Monday 24 August 2015. Online Form - Win England v Ireland rugby tickets @telegraph
